# ARK-Packages/community/
#
# This directory is for community-maintained packages.
# Any contributor may submit a package here by following the
# contribution guide in README.md.
#
# Community packages follow the same ARKBUILD + pkginfo.json format
# as core packages, but are maintained by third-party contributors
# rather than the ARK OS Core Team.
#
# Quality bar:
#   - Passes the Forge CI/CD pipeline (same as core)
#   - pkginfo.json must include accurate contributor details
#   - Package must build cleanly against musl on Alpine Edge
#
# Submit a PR with your package directory to get started.
